; padding:0;\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\"><table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:15px 0 20px 0;\"><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-title\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:40px; line-height:46px; color:#09354B; font-weight:bold;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBedankt voor je interesse in Eneco!\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\"><table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:15px 40px 10px 0;\"><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:12px; line-height:18px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold;\"></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\"><table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:10px 40px;\"><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#000000; padding-bottom:20px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBeste Deys,<br /><br /> Zoals afgesproken, hebben we een duurzaam én voordelig contractvoorstel voor je opgemaakt.<br /><br /> Wil je genieten van onze scherpe prijzen van deze maand? Bevestig dit zeker vóór de laatste dag van de maand waarin deze e-mail is verstuurd*. Als je pas volgende maand bevestigt, zullen namelijk nieuwe prijzen gelden.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br /> Wacht dus niet te lang om het te bevestigen. Dat kan heel eenvoudig via deze link:\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\"><table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:20px 0 20px 0;\"><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"#EA754F\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:18px; line-height:24px; color:#FFFFFF; padding:10px 30px; border-radius:5px;\"><a href=\"https://my.eneco.be/nl/Shop/Continue/2026121-II4AS0M060316\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:none;\">Bekijk jouw persoonlijk voorstel</a></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\"><table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:20px 40px 50px 40px;\"><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:24px; line-height:30px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; padding-bottom:10px;\">Heb je nog vragen?</td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#000000;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBel gerust iedere werkdag tussen 8 en 18 uur naar \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<strong>015 68 68 58</strong>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tof stel je vraag via ons \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://eneco.be/helpmij\" style=\"color:#D21242; text-decoration:underline;\">contactformulier</a>.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br /><br /><br />Met vriendelijke groeten,<br /><br />Bert Clinckers<br /><strong>Gedelegeerd Bestuurder</strong></td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#000000;\"><br />*Hou er rekening mee dat als je voorstel Eneco Zon &amp; Wind of Eneco Aardgas Vast bevat, dit momenteel beperkt voorradig is. Op de tariefkaart vind je meer info.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br /><br /></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"wrapper\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"outerpadding\"><table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"devicewidth\" style=\"width:600px;\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:20px 0 0;\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"innerpadding\"><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"><table width=\"195\" border=\"0\" align=\"left\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt;\" class=\"fullwidth\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-b